# PLACEHOLDER — replace with the real RSA public key before building.
# Run scripts/generate-license-keys.sh to generate the key pair.
# Copy the PUBLIC key here and keep the PRIVATE key in your cloud .env as CLIENT_LICENSE_PRIVATE_KEY.
#
# Expected format:
# -----BEGIN RSA PUBLIC KEY-----
# MIIBCgKCAQEA...
# -----END RSA PUBLIC KEY-----
